members.name: getTypeParameters
members.comment: Returns an array of TypeVariable objects that represent the type variables declared by the generic declaration represented by this GenericDeclaration object, in declaration order. Returns an array of length 0 if the underlying generic declaration declares no type variables.

throws: GenericSignatureFormatError - if the generic signature of this generic declaration does not conform to the format specified in The Java Virtual Machine Specification
return: an array of TypeVariable objects that represent the type variables declared by this generic declaration

name: java.lang.reflect.GenericDeclaration
comment: A common interface for all entities that declare type variables.
